✅ 1. SMOOTH TRANSITION ANIMATIONS
   ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   
   ✓ Previous: Abrupt element appearance (CSS had no transitions)
   ✓ Now:     Smooth 0.3-0.6 second animations
   
   Animations Implemented:
   ├─ slideUp (0.6s)     → Cards, buttons, forms slide in from bottom
   ├─ slideDown (0.4s)   → Header, alerts slide from top
   ├─ pulse-red (2s)     → Alert pulsing effect
   ├─ shake (0.5s)       → Error banner shake animation
   ├─ bounce-soft (2s)   → Logo animated bounce
   ├─ glow-pulse (2s)    → Text glow effect
   ├─ fadeIn (0.3s)      → Smooth fade effect
   └─ bounce-soft (2s)   → SS logo subtle bounce
   
   Easing Functions Used:
   ├─ cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)  → Elastic, natural motion
   ├─ ease-out                             → Smooth deceleration
   ├─ ease-in-out                          → Smooth acceleration & deceleration
   └─ linear                               → Consistent speed
   
   Stagger Delays:
   ├─ 0.0s  → Primary elements
   ├─ 0.1s  → Secondary elements
   ├─ 0.2s  → Tertiary elements
   └─ 0.4s+ → Delayed animations
   
   Where Applied:
   ├─ Login page → slideUp animation on mount
   ├─ Cards      → slideUp on load, hover effects
   ├─ Buttons    → slideUp on load
   ├─ Alerts     → slideDown with stagger
   ├─ Banners    → slideDown or shake
   ├─ Header     → slideDown on page load
   ├─ Glass boxes→ slideUp with glow
   └─ Metrics    → slideUp with stagger


